Blacknose coefficient effects Model 3

### TEMPBOTM
pd <- data.frame(YEAR = "2013",
                 MONTH = "Aug",
                 STARTLAT = rep(mean(blacknose$STARTLAT, na.rm=TRUE), 3152),
                 STARTLON = rep(mean(blacknose$STARTLON, na.rm=TRUE), 3152),
                 AVG.DEPTH = rep(mean(blacknose$AVG.DEPTH, na.rm=TRUE), 3152), 
                 TEMPBOTM = rep(mean(blacknose$TEMPBOTM, na.rm=TRUE), 3152),
                 FLUOROBOTM = rep(mean(blacknose$FLUOROBOTM, na.rm=TRUE), 3152),
                 TURBBOTM = rep(mean(blacknose$TURBBOTM, na.rm=TRUE), 3152),
                 OXYBOTM = rep(mean(blacknose$OXYBOTM, na.rm=TRUE), 3152),
                 SALBOTM = rep(mean(blacknose$SALBOTM, na.rm=TRUE), 3152),
                 dombot4 = "Mud",
                 dombot8 = " Mud-Dominant")

pd$TEMPBOTM = seq(0, 100,length = 3152)

pv <- predict(bn.mod3, newdata = pd, type = "response")

with(blacknose, 
     plot(TEMPBOTM, cpe, 
          pch = 19, cex = 0.25,
          col = 3))
lines(pd$TEMPBOTM,pv, 
      col = 2)

pv <- predict(bn.mod3, newdata = pd, type = "link", se = TRUE)

with(blacknose, 
     plot(TEMPBOTM, cpe, 
          pch = 19, cex = 0.25,
          col = 3))
lines(pd$TEMPBOTM,
      exp(pv$fit + 2*pv$se.fit), 
      col = 2)
lines(pd$TEMPBOTM,
      exp(pv$fit - 2*pv$se.fit), 
      col = 2)

### TEMPBOTM
pd <- data.frame(YEAR = "2013",
                 STARTLAT = mean(sharpnose$STARTLAT, na.rm = TRUE),
                 STARTLON = mean(sharpnose$STARTLON, na.rm = TRUE),
                 AVG.DEPTH = mean(sharpnose$AVG.DEPTH, na.rm = TRUE),
                 TEMPBOTM = seq(0, 100,length = 1278),
                 FLUOROBOTM = mean(sharpnose$FLUOROBOTM, na.rm = TRUE),
                 OXYBOTM = mean(sharpnose$OXYBOTM, na.rm = TRUE))

pv <- predict(sn.mod1.9, newdata = pd, type = "response")

with(sharpnose, 
     plot(TEMPBOTM, cpe, 
          pch = 19, cex = 0.25,
          col = 3))
lines(pd$TEMPBOTM,pv, 
      col = 2)

pv <- predict(sn.mod1.9, newdata = pd, type = "link", se = TRUE)

with(sharpnose, 
     plot(TEMPBOTM, cpe, 
          pch = 19, cex = 0.25,
          col = 3))
lines(pd$TEMPBOTM,
      exp(pv$fit + 2*pv$se.fit), 
      col = 2)
lines(pd$TEMPBOTM,
      exp(pv$fit - 2*pv$se.fit), 
      col = 2)
